rows.label: qst004102_msg0001
rows.name:
Go straight from Torigo till you
see Twin Trunks Hill. The Tirkin
Turf is on top of that tree there.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0002
rows.name:
They've built some impressive
structures, so you'll know
when you're there.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0101
rows.name: Made it back in one piece, eh?

rows.label: qst004102_msg0102
rows.name:
Mind telling me how the Revenge
Tirkin launched their attacks?

rows.label: qst004102_msg0103
rows.name:
I know, I know. But I've got
to give my superior some kind
of report to keep them happy.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0104
rows.name: Whew. Sounds like a rough bunch indeed.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0105
rows.name:
That info'll come in very handy
if they ever attack us again.

rows.label: qst004102_msg0106
rows.name:
Thanks for that. Here's your reward,
as promised: one Filament Globe!
